item.description:
**Added a third tee time at 12:40pm**

Hi All,

If anyone is staying local for Memorial Day weekend, I have a couple of tee times at Black Swan Country Club in Georgetown, MA for Sunday, May 26th at 12:20 & 12:30.

Fun and challenging course. Driving range and nice club house for those who like to grab a drink after the round. Voted best public golf course the past two years by North Shore Magazine. Easy to get to off Rte. 95.

Greens Fee is $67 for 18 holes and includes cart. Join if you can. Cancellations required by 9:00am Saturday, May 25th.

For more course info:

http://golf.blackswancountryclub.com/index.html

Course Location: 258 Andover Street, Georgetown, MA
